parameters: Mage Relm: I think this is the designated place.

Priestess Sophia: Rather than beautiful, this place feels
eerie, doesn't it?

Thief Nora: Where could Albus-san be? There doesn't seem to
be any place suitable for him to enter, right?

Clea: I believe that someone who can create such elaborate
traps would never leave anything to chance.

Mage Relm: As Clea-san said, there was a crystal left
together with the invitation.
Mage Relm: I think this is the key to meeting Albus.

Mage Relm: We have come here following your instructions,
with the invitation and crystal.
Mage Relm: Now, please lead us to your place!

Mage Relm: Th-This is... an incredible vortex of magical
power...!?

Mage Relm: Kuuh, stay back! Hurry, everyone, gather
together!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Bard: Hey, you guys are really interesting.

Mage Relm: Oh, it's you again! We haven't done anything, you
know!

Bard: We made a promise not to leave this place, so we're
staying here, and his soul is also staying here.

Bard: Please don't cause any trouble. It's already been
decided that he can't leave.

Bard: Yes, as long as you guys keep that promise, I'll leave
this place alone.
